                        <interp inst="t18390812-name-140" type="surname" value="HARRIS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390812-name-140" type="given" value="MARY ANN"></interp>MARY ANN HARRIS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am eight years old. I was out with my little sister in my arms—she had a necklace on—the prisoner came up and gave me one bunch of currants, and my sister two—he took my sister in his arms, and nursed her, and then gave her to me—when we got home, my father missed the necklace—I am sure she had it on when the prisoner took her—I knew him before by seeing him about.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390812-name-141" type="witnessName">
